name: mutl
author: iarkn
description:
Contains useful (probably) features or utilities:
  - console
  - unit spawner
  - entity display
  - and more...

Press F9 to access utilities menu on desktop. On mobile, tap the button with a wrench icon once you have loaded a world.

For more information, please visit <https://github.com/Receptea/mind-util/wiki>.
